          <li><strong class="text-white">Change the player color.</strong> Try <code class="text-[#ffcc00] bg-[#ffcc0015] rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-bold font-mono">(255, 0, 0)</code> for red or <code class="text-[#ffcc00] bg-[#ffcc0015] rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-bold font-mono">(0, 255, 0)</code> for green. Pick your hero&#x27;s color.</li>
