        </ol>

        <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">The full code is in <code class="text-[#ffcc00] bg-[#ffcc0015] rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-bold font-mono">dungeon.py</code>.</p>

        <h2 class="font-['Bangers'] text-2xl text-[#ffcc00] border-b-4 border-dashed border-[#ff00ff30] pb-2 mt-10 mb-4">Run It!</h2>

