        </ol>

        <h2 class="font-['Bangers'] text-2xl text-[#ffcc00] border-b-4 border-dashed border-[#ff00ff30] pb-2 mt-10 mb-4">Challenge</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">Add a <strong class="text-white">second phase</strong> to the boss fight. When the boss drops below half health, it enters &quot;rage mode&quot;: it moves faster in chase phase (every 8 frames instead of 15), charges deal 5 damage instead of 3, and its color changes to bright red. Display &quot;RAGE MODE!&quot; text on screen when this happens.</p>
