self.screen.blit(vol_text, (SCREEN_WIDTH - 160, SCREEN_HEIGHT - 25))</code></pre>

        <h3 class="font-['Bangers'] text-xl text-[#ff69b4] mt-8 mb-3">The Full Game</h3>

        <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">The complete file is <code class="text-[#ffcc00] bg-[#ffcc0015] rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-bold font-mono">dungeon.py</code> in this folder. It includes everything from Lesson 26 (sprites) plus the full sound system.</p>

