        <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">You&#x27;ll see the start screen first. Press SPACE to begin. Move with arrows or WASD, attack with Space. Press Escape to pause. Beat the boss to find the staircase to Level 2!</p>

        <h2 class="font-['Bangers'] text-2xl text-[#ffcc00] border-b-4 border-dashed border-[#ff00ff30] pb-2 mt-10 mb-4">Experiments</h2>

