        <h2 class="font-['Bangers'] text-2xl text-[#ffcc00] border-b-4 border-dashed border-[#ff00ff30] pb-2 mt-10 mb-4">Challenge</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">Add a <strong class="text-white">trading system</strong>: when both players stand next to each other and one presses T, they drop their selected inventory item on the ground. The other player can pick it up. This lets players share health potions strategically.</p>
