        <h2 class="font-['Bangers'] text-2xl text-[#ffcc00] border-b-4 border-dashed border-[#ff00ff30] pb-2 mt-10 mb-4">Everything Comes Together</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-4">You&#x27;ve spent this whole course building up skills one by one. Variables, loops, classes, Pygame, procedural generation, combat, loot, co-op... and now isometric rendering with depth sorting.</p>

