        <h2 class="font-['Bangers'] text-2xl text-[#ffcc00] border-b-4 border-dashed border-[#ff00ff30] pb-2 mt-10 mb-4">Experiments</h2>

        <ol class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-6 list-decimal pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong class="text-white">Boss room</strong> -- add a boss that spawns in the largest room. Give it 3x health and a unique color. It drops a special item when defeated.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Ranged attack</strong> -- add a projectile that travels in the direction the player faces. It needs its own depth value that updates as it moves across the grid.</li>
